Simple example of using Neography together with the neo4j-cypher gem.

See http://maxdemarzi.com/2012/01/04/getting-started-with-ruby-and-neo4j/ and http://maxdemarzi.com/2012/01/07/cypher-with-neography/
for the original example without the neo4j-cypher gem.

To Run:
rvm use 1.9.3 (for example)
bundle install
rake neo4j:install
rake neo4j:start

ruby foaf.rb